{"tid":241414,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[點睇] 又一個沒有金像的導演—葉偉信","createTime":"2017-05-13T06:58:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-14T05:52:44.000Z","uid":34701,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5f0dbf262f513f1bd80452737312ec4f2e20ed19","tid":241414,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T06:58:23.000Z","msg":"提起葉偉信，最出名嘅作品一定係葉問系列<br />\n但佢以前嘅輕鬆小品戲都好值得一睇再睇，自己就好鍾意生化壽屍，爆裂刑警同2002<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喪屍題材嘅戲喺香港算係比較少有，仲有係拍攝場地係一個富有本土特色嘅小商場，睇落更加有代入感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n爆裂刑警呢套戲更加係令到羅蘭姐成為香港史上最老嘅金像影后<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鎮宇做有病嘅角色都做得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2002就係驚嚇得嚟又有好多笑位(羅家英好正)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我直頭覺得算係一套高質港產鬼片添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外有套茱麗葉與梁山泊都好多人話正，但我仲未有機會睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一句講晒，我覺得佢都係一個above average嘅導演<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你哋又點睇葉偉信？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26bc22ed3c1e41f4fb590422f44f4f69cf80013b","tid":241414,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T06:59:55.000Z","msg":"琴日講完邱禮濤，今日順便講埋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"356aad29ec6a22d28a1d5dbdaed44fd7b7af23fd","tid":241414,"uid":43331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T07:05:27.000Z","msg":"上維基睇<br />\n<br />\n原來佢都出幾多高質小品<br />\n<br />\n乾柴烈火 2002 五個嚇鬼的小年都幾好睇"},{"pid":"0f141f2ce8b45bc5ad26a161c1f8b565ba77c693","tid":241414,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T07:26:19.000Z","msg":"一拍合拍片咪on9化哂囉"},{"pid":"0452c5ba7b0c5c6362aaff773e7f0cb85dd37481","tid":241414,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T07:28:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上維基睇<br />\n<br />\n原來佢都出幾多高質小品<br />\n<br />\n乾柴烈火 2002 五個嚇鬼的小年都幾好睇</blockquote><br />\n係<br />\n絕對係蔗渣價錢燒鵝味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"951adc00e873426d7c3c3943b35824e019a33163","tid":241414,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T07:30:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一拍合拍片咪on9化哂囉</blockquote><br />\n冇計，大趨勢係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過幾欣賞佢搵泰臣拍葉問3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2738bfb607b4b8a377fd61d2e00cb79e6a0b19c0","tid":241414,"uid":64953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T08:27:45.000Z","msg":"五個嚇鬼的少年係咪最後尾玩爆旋陀螺o個套??"},{"pid":"118286de24abbf38c8f5e8eaedd18d81875add0b","tid":241414,"uid":43331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T11:21:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>五個嚇鬼的少年係咪最後尾玩爆旋陀螺o個套??</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41a933d1d0012b5078a02c407fcd142dd87fac6a","tid":241414,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T12:22:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://lh5.ggpht.com/_x9bPXf77xGc/TSXM7X6OSMI/AAAAAAAALpY/AI1K43-w05k/s576/Bullets29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flh5.ggpht.com%2F_x9bPXf77xGc%2FTSXM7X6OSMI%2FAAAAAAAALpY%2FAI1K43-w05k%2Fs576%2FBullets29.jpg&h=c7e5b486&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿mike<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2a41b793b6941f53ec756c6b8e83581c9a02b09","tid":241414,"uid":57007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T12:46:59.000Z","msg":"呢排報紙先提番誤人子弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b88cfc0b809df5612d8961fc768a050a924715","tid":241414,"uid":11185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T14:33:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img1.readhouse.net/20161104/14782256268187961.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.readhouse.net%2F20161104%2F14782256268187961.jpg&h=19f079df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a7aca0f234f1b4025df5810a0bfd67d6f9eac52","tid":241414,"uid":34970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T14:37:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img1.readhouse.net/20161104/14782256268187961.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.readhouse.net%2F20161104%2F14782256268187961.jpg&h=19f079df&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n殺破狼無論故事定打鬥都係上品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f530694781046bf8e46e4c0ec3fcd58f5823e022","tid":241414,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T14:55:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://img1.readhouse.net/20161104/14782256268187961.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.readhouse.net%2F20161104%2F14782256268187961.jpg&h=19f079df&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n殺破狼無論故事定打鬥都係上品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n葉偉信拍打鬥場面真心好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全靠佢先可以帶起葉問熱潮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢同丹爺都算係黃金組合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"864b1f6437f99c1f0d8126af4c2a8bed746cf3d0","tid":241414,"uid":56188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T15:49:20.000Z","msg":"大城小事我幾鐘意"},{"pid":"d349b55640b4480b7ba02f32e520d7526828d61f","tid":241414,"uid":39812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T22:17:16.000Z","msg":"有料 但係而家淨係玩商業片發揮唔到<br />\n以前小品年代嘅幾個葉偉信常用嘅象徵（可樂 食飯 仲有啲我醒唔起）<br />\n去到葉問年代只剩低食飯呢個符號<br />\n一方面睇得出佢唔係完全拋棄佢小品年代想講嘅嘢<br />\n另一方面睇就係佢都真係拋走咗好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最發揮佢商業片上嘅功力我覺得係甄氏武打片而唔係葉問<br />\n而咁多套最好嘅應該係爆裂刑警<br />\n但係對我嚟講最深刻係茱麗葉與梁山泊<br />\nNo coke no hope<br />\n無所謂啦<br />\n等我，我返嚟食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KUJK4P2QdqI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKUJK4P2QdqI&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=43375120\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KUJK4P2QdqI</a>"},{"pid":"6083c800d208329b5b327ade833fa16de432c069","tid":241414,"uid":39812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T22:18:51.000Z","msg":"講起葉偉信可以順便講下鄭保瑞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ebb0657bc98b3c6de0e62353a1196a1dd9220f","tid":241414,"uid":60977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T00:49:48.000Z","msg":"爆裂係幾好睇"},{"pid":"c468d60fe9764cbb2070df7e25ffab5bfbccb054","tid":241414,"uid":48473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T05:51:28.000Z","msg":"殺破狼真係好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我諗我睇左十次都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"091fd8d814770485dad847821a498bdcba5cc125","tid":241414,"uid":48473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T05:52:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://img1.readhouse.net/20161104/14782256268187961.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.readhouse.net%2F20161104%2F14782256268187961.jpg&h=19f079df&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n殺破狼無論故事定打鬥都係上品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢幕真係睇100次都唔厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}